{
  "title": "Rich Spicy Middle Eastern Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A spicy and flavorful Middle Eastern dish featuring lamb, taleggio, and beurre-monte, perfect for a lazy Sunday. This low-calorie-friendly recipe is made with wholesome ingredients.",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
  "diet": [
